verses.verse: Praise<WH1984> you the LORD.<WH3050> Praise<WH1984> God<WH410> in his sanctuary:<WH6944> praise<WH1984> him in the firmament<WH7549> of his power.<WH5797>
Praise<WH1984> him for his mighty<WH1369> acts: praise<WH1984> him according to his excellent<WH7230> greatness.<WH1433>
Praise<WH1984> him with the sound<WH8629> of the trumpet:<WH7782> praise<WH1984> him with the psaltery<WH5035> and harp.<WH3658>
Praise<WH1984> him with the tambourine<WH8596> and dance:<WH4234> praise<WH1984> him with stringed<WH4482> instruments<WH4482> and organs.<WH5748>
Praise<WH1984> him on the loud<WH8085> cymbals:<WH6767> praise<WH1984> him on the high<WH8643> sounding<WH8643> cymbals.<WH6767>
